---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="About | Homelab Fit">
  <section class="page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Independent homelab compatibility notes</h1>
    <p>Homelab Fit is a static knowledge base prototype for source-backed Proxmox hardware, storage, networking, and passthrough decisions.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-block">
    <h2>Independence</h2>
    <p>This site is not affiliated with, sponsored by, or endorsed by Proxmox Server Solutions GmbH, Intel, AMD, Minisforum, Beelink, or other vendors. Product names identify hardware and software contexts.</p>
    <h2>Quality policy</h2>
    <p>Published pages should be source-backed, hardware-specific, and practical. Draft pages should stay noindex until they have facts, risks, verification checks, and source metadata.</p>
    <h2>Expansion rule</h2>
    <p>The site should expand only after search indexing and query data show which page types deserve more production volume.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
